    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! We're talking pristine condition inside and out\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and has been pampered since day one. I'm so sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner so happy! Feel free to reach out with any questions! \u2728",
