    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish free of any stone chips, scratches, or swirls, while the interior still retains that distinctive new-car scent with supple leather seats showing zero bolster wear. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; the engine runs with whisper-quiet precision and the transmission shifts seamlessly. Garage-kept under a climate-controlled cover and maintained exclusively by certified master technicians, it comes with a complete, documented service history. From the flawless alloy wheels to the pristine undercarriage, this is an investment-grade example that satisfies even the most discerning collector. It needs absolutely nothing but a new driver.",
